FFmpeg README
-------------

1) Documentation
----------------

* Read the documentation in the doc/ directory in git.
  You can also view it online at http://ffmpeg.org/documentation.html

2) Licensing
------------

* See the LICENSE file.

3) Build and Install
--------------------

* See the INSTALL file.

4) ffplay
---------
ffplay requires sdl, install sdl using brew install sdl before running configure.sh

http://www.libsdl.org/


